Extracted Variables:
- x: number of wired headphones produced
- y: number of wireless headphones produced

Definitions:
- x: number of wired headphones produced
- y: number of wireless headphones produced

Constraints:
- Wired Team Constraint: x \leq 100 (The wired team can make at most 100 wired headphones per day)
- Wireless Team Constraint: y \leq 170 (The wireless team can make at most 170 wireless headphones per day)
- Audio Testing Machine Constraint: x + y \leq 150 (The audio testing machine can make a maximum of 150 headphones per day)

Objective:
- Maximize profit: Maximize 50x + 20y (Profit per wired headphone is $50 and profit per wireless headphone is $20)
